data.title: Grand Duke Paul Alexandrovich and Grand Duchess Alexandra Georgievna, when Princess Alexandra of Greece
data.meta_description: Photograph of Grand Duke Paul Alexandrovich (1860-1919) and Princess Alexandra of Greece (1870-1891), later Grand Duchess Alexandra Georgievna. Grand Duke Paul is sitting on a sofa, wearing military uniform and holding a hat. Princess Alexandra is standing beside him to the right, her right arm around his shoulder. She is holding an umbrella and gloves in her left hand. There is a chair to the right and a painted backdrop behind.Grand Duke Paul Alexandrovich was the youngest child of Alexander II, Emperor...
